quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  99,1,When the earth is shaken with its earthquake
  99,2,And the earth brings out its burdens
  99,3,"And man wonders, \"What is the matter with it"
  99,4,"That Day it [the earth] will relate its stories"
  99,5,Because your Lord inspires it
  99,6,That Day mankind will proceed in groups to be shown their deeds
  99,7,"Then whoever does [even] an atom's weight of good deed will see it"
  99,8,"And whoever does [even] an atom's weight of bad deed will see it"